quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  23,33,"“Ndipo akuluakulu a mwa anthu ake amene adali osakhulupirira, ndikutsutsa za kukumana ndi tsiku la chimaliziro, omwe tidawapatsa kulemera pa moyo wa padziko lapansi, adati: “Uyu saali kanthu, koma ndi munthu monga inu; amadya zimene inu mumadya, ndi kumwa zomwe inu mumamwa"
  23,34,"“Koma ngati mumvera munthu wonga inu, ndiye kuti mukhala otaika (oluza)"
  23,35,"“Kodi akukulonjezani kuti mukadzafa ndikusanduka dothi ndi mafupa, mudzaukitsidwanso (m’manda)"
  23,36,"“Sizingachitike, sizingachitike, zimene mukulonjezedwazi"
  23,37,“Palibe (moyo wina) koma moyo wathu wapadziko lapansiwu basi! Tikufa ndiponso kukhala ndi moyo! Ndipo sitidzaukitsidwa m’manda
  23,38,"“Uyu saali kanthu (amene akudzitcha kuti ndi Mtumiki) koma ndi munthu basi, akupekera Allah bodza, ndipo ife sitimkhulupirira.”"
  23,39,"“(Mtumikiyo) adati: “E Mbuye wanga! Ndipulumutseni pachifukwa chakuti anditsutsa.”"
  23,40,"“(Allah) adati: “Posachedwapa akhala odzinena.”"
  23,41,"“Choncho, mkuwe wa (chilango) choonadi udawaononga, ndipo tidawachita ngati zinyalala (zongotengedwa ndi madzi). Choncho, kuonongeka kudatsimikizika pa anthu osalungama"
  23,42,“Ndipo titatero tidalenga mibadwo ina pambuyo pawo
  23,43,“Palibe mtundu ungaifulumizitse kapena kuichedwetsa nthawi yake yofera
  23,44,"“Kenaka tidatuma atumiki Athu motsatizana; (wina pambuyo pa mnzake). Ndipo mbadwo uliwonse pamene adaufikira mtumiki wake, udamtsutsa; ndipo tidawaononga motsatana; ndipo tidawachita kukhala nkhani (za anthu.) Ndipo kuonongeka kudatsimikizika pa anthu osakhulupirira"
  23,45,"“Zitatero tidatuma Mûsa ndi m’bale wake Harun ndi zozizwitsa Zathu, ndi umboni woonekera poyera"
  23,46,“Kwa Farawo ndi nduna zake. Koma onse adadzitukumula; ndipo adali anthu odzikweza
  23,47,"“Ndipo adati: “Ha! Tikhulupirire anthu awiri onga ife, omwe mtundu wawo ndi akapolo athu!”"
  23,48,"“Choncho adawatsutsa onse awiri, ndipo adali m’gulu la oonongedwa"
  23,49,“Ndipo ndithu Mûsa tidampatsa buku kuti iwo aongoke
  23,50,"“Ndipo tidamchita mwana wa Mariya ndi mayi wake kukhala chisonyezo (choonetsa kukhoza kwathu). Ndipo tidawapatsa malo othawirapo, pachikweza, chokhazikika pomwenso padali akasupe"